reviews.reviewText: 5 stars ⭐️ for this set of TSA approved travel bottles. Contains 2 spray bottles, 4 small round cream jars and 4 silicone travels bottles (for lotion or body wash). Also contains labels, 2 mini funnels and 2 little spoons for the cream jars. This is a very good set and perfect for air travel, because everything is TSA approved size.
